A BILL ENTITLED
1 AN ACT concerning
2 Health Care Malpractice Claims – Health Care Provider – Definition
3 FOR the purpose of altering the definition of “health care provider” to include certain
4 employees, agents, or contractors of a hospital in provisions relating to health care
5 malpractice claims; and generally relating to health care malpractice claims.
